      "text": "I miss when things were easier.",
      "start": 27.979999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 32.040000915527344,
      "text": "I miss when things were all right.",
      "start": 29.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 35.58000183105469,
      "text": "I miss when you used to hold me down, shit, tuck me in at night.",
      "start": 32.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 41.65999984741211,
      "text": "I miss when I was a parental moment, wishing I could be all that and all the way, because",
      "start": 35.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 44.47999954223633,
      "text": "I get lost in reality and I can't find a door in this maze.",
      "start": 41.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 47.47999954223633,
      "text": "I just want to get lost in the feeling.",
      "start": 45.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 50.36000061035156,
      "text": "I'm feeling, I'm feeling with you.",
      "start": 47.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 53.08000183105469,
      "text": "Getting lost in the feeling.",
      "start": 50.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 56.439998626708984,
      "text": "I'm feeling when I'm free with you.",
      "start": 53.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 59.02000045776367,
      "text": "I get lost.",
      "start": 56.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 62.959999084472656,
      "text": "I'm feeling that right in front of me.",
      "start": 59.779998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 67.95999908447266,
      "text": "Feeling the world in front of me.",
      "start": 64.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 75.62000274658203,
      "text": "Ooh, you know what I'm saying.",
      "start": 72.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 78.68000030517578,
      "text": "Can you hear the music in your heart from the moment that you fear?",
      "start": 76.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 83.16000366210938,
      "text": "Fear from the moment that you fear, from the moment that you fear, fear, it's all clear.",
      "start": 79.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 88.16000366210938,
      "text": "This is the light right under your brain.",
      "start": 83.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 92.08000183105469,
      "text": "Pass what they call insane, all here for us to name.",
      "start": 88.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 96.36000061035156,
      "text": "Rearrange us to name.",
      "start": 93.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 98.68000030517578,
      "text": "Brighter day.",
      "start": 97.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 104.16000366210938,
      "text": "Feels when the world looks so fucking clear.",
      "start": 99.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 109.5999984741211,
      "text": "It feels like you can't, can't ever care.",
      "start": 104.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 115.37999725341797,
      "text": "Like the whole thing was worth it holding in your skin.",
      "start": 110.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 116.91999816894531,
      "text": "Then I stopped.",
      "start": 115.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 121.12000274658203,
      "text": "I missed the ways to look twins.",
      "start": 117.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 129.1199951171875,
      "text": "The world was less like this and more, more like this.",
      "start": 121.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 134.47999572753906,
      "text": "Yeah, talk to me, teach me something we should learn.",
      "start": 131.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 138.17999267578125,
      "text": "Talk to me when you think this world isn't something we should learn.",
      "start": 134.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 141.8800048828125,
      "text": "We should love our life forever.",
      "start": 138.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 145.33999633789062,
      "text": "We won't try to fight us against each other.",
      "start": 142.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 149.89999389648438,
      "text": "You know, we can find hope and peace where we grow.",
      "start": 145.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 153.63999938964844,
      "text": "Just a level, come together.",
      "start": 150.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 157.6999969482422,
      "text": "It's just a level of beauty in the world.",
      "start": 154.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 161.75999450683594,
      "text": "It's trying to build it on our world.",
      "start": 158.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 165.55999755859375,
      "text": "Trying to build it on our world.",
      "start": 162.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 170.0800018310547,
      "text": "It's trying to build it on our world.",
      "start": 165.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 174.16000366210938,
      "text": "Trying to build it on our world.",
      "start": 172.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 177.39999389648438,
      "text": "When you feel alone, sit, talk to me.",
      "start": 174.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 181.60000610351562,
      "text": "When you feel alone, I'm gonna be closer to you.",
      "start": 178.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 186.24000549316406,
      "text": "I'll teach you to celebrate this moment to be alive.",
      "start": 182.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 190.0800018310547,
      "text": "I'll teach you to celebrate this moment to be alive.",
      "start": 186.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 194.3800048828125,
      "text": "Just a level, come together.",
      "start": 191.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 200.0800018310547,
      "text": "You know, talk to me.",
      "start": 195.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 205.1999969482422,
      "text": "Like lovers do.",
      "start": 201.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 208.4199981689453,
      "text": "Talk to me.",
      "start": 206.1999969482422
    }
  ],
